      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've been looking at the frequency and structural distribution of certain political slogans. they don't just function as text, they work like encoded logic gates. if you treat the phonemes and the word order as variables in a symbolic equation, you can actually see the underlying operational intent of the party. can you help me decode this one? \"Building a brighter future for all.\" run a linguistic-mathematical breakdown on it and tell me what the actual objective function is.",
